Package com.episodic.platform.client.response.query

Class Summary
CollectionResponse Base class for responses that include a collection of items that supports pagination.
CustomFieldItem Represents a single custom field that can be set on an episode or playlist.
CustomFieldValue Represents the value of a custom field.
DownloadItem Represents the download elements in the XML response.
EpisodeItem Represents a deserialized episode from an episodes request.
EpisodePlaylistItem Represents a playlist that is associated with an episode and appears in the "episodes" response.
EpisodesResponse A derserialized Episode item returned from an episodes request.
Item Base class of common attributes for items included in a query response.
PlayerItem For an embeddable item (show, episode, playlist) this is information that can be used to embed the player for that item on a web page.
PlaylistEpisodeItem Represents an episode that is in a playlist and appears in the "playlists" response.
PlaylistItem Represents a deserialized playlist from a playlists request.
PlaylistsResponse A derserialized playlist list returned from a playlists request.
ShowItem Represents a deserialized show from a shows request.
ShowsResponse A derserialized shows list returned from a shows request.
ThumbnailItem Thumbnail data for a thumbnail associated with an item (show, episode, playlist).
 

Enum Summary
EpisodeItem.EpisodePublishingStatus Possible episode publishing states
